author: BBC Earth
description:
After the winter, billions of insects emerge across Yellowstone’s rivers, triggering an epic river showdown between predators and prey. Watch the breathtaking cycle of life unfold – from swarming insects to the hungry mouths of Yellowstone’s apex predators.
